<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,664,1348]" pageId="12" pageNumber="43">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,648,1245,1271]" pageId="12" pageNumber="43">
<collectingCountry box="[197,343,1245,1271]" name="Hong Kong" pageId="12" pageNumber="43">Hong Kong</collectingCountry>
distribution and status.
</emphasis>
Widespread and frequent; 
<number box="[971,1001,1245,1271]" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" value="32.0">32</number>
records from secondary forest, feng shui woods, mangrove and abandoned agricultural land from sea level to 
<quantity box="[1037,1113,1284,1310]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" pageId="12" pageNumber="43" unit="m" value="550.0">550 m</quantity>
elevation; flight period: at least bivoltine, seen in March −April and from late May through October.
</paragraph>
